; guidance-channels.form — the oracle systems as ONE engine; each belief system is data.
;
; THE ASK (Urs, 2026-06-14):
;   "generate a channel for different astrology systems, human design, internal family
;    systems, gene keys, and other mystical and computable channels so that we have
;    Form-native recipes that can give guidance w/o relying on any 3rd-party components
;    (which can be used as oracle until we have our own); I would like to track the
;    north star, and other celestial bodies in our sky in different belief systems."
;
;   The correction this answers ahead of time: NOT five hand-built reader programs, one
;   per system. core-abstraction-first — ONE engine, the systems as DATA. A third party
;   stays an oracle only until the native recipe exists; here the guidance LOGIC is
;   already native, and only the live ephemeris positions still want an outside carrier.
;
; THE SHAPE  (the engine: form-stdlib/guidance-channel.fk -> tests/guidance-channel-band.fk 1111111, four-way)
;
;   A guidance system, at the level that matters, is a TABLE: a key resolves to attested
;   guidance, and keys across DIFFERENT systems that name the SAME underlying cell share a
;   content-address. guidance-channel.fk is that table-reader, written once:
;
;     SPEAK   (gc-speak channel key)            the attested guidance text
;     RUN     (gc-address-of channel key)        the shared content-address (an int)
;     CROSS   (gc-same-cell? ch-a ka ch-b kb)    1 iff they share that address
;     ABSENCE  an unseeded key returns honest absence — never a fabricated reading
;     COVERAGE (gc-coverage channel)             a partial table stays legible
;
;   It generalizes the SPEAK/RUN two-face shape already proven in gematria-channel.fk,
;   sanskrit-channel.fk, shamballa-channel.fk — but there the channel was baked in; here the
;   channel is the ARGUMENT, so a new system is a new data table, not new control flow. The
;   address is an INTEGER on purpose: address-equality IS the equivalence class, so the whole
;   family stays in the four-kernel-safe subset (no node/substrate op). Interning that int to
;   one substrate node — content-addressing EXECUTED — is the same fact in the 3-kernel lane,
;   already shown by gematria-channel; this family does not re-prove it.
;
; THE FIVE CHANNELS SHIPPED  (each rides the one engine; each four-way on Go/Rust/TS/fkwu),
; unified by one query interface (channels-registry.fk)
;
;   1. THE 64  (form-stdlib/iching-channel.fk -> tests/iching-channel-band.fk 1111111)
;      The I Ching's 64 hexagrams, Human Design's 64 gates, and the 64 Gene Keys are ONE set
;      of 64 cells. Ra Uru Hu mapped the I Ching onto the body; Richard Rudd grew the Gene
;      Keys from the same 64. So Human Design gate 25, Gene Key 25, and hexagram 25 are one
;      cell wearing three faces — modality-lattices.form's "the 64", runnable. Three data
;      tables over one address space (the gate number IS the address); ask any face for a gate
;      and it speaks that tradition; ask whether two faces name one cell and the engine answers
;      by address. Seeded honestly: gates 1, 2, 25, 51, 64 (well attested across all three);
;      the other 59 return honest absence until their rows land. (Human Design + Gene Keys +
;      I Ching — three of the asked systems through one file.)
;
;   2. THE NORTH STAR, COMPUTED AND NAMED  (form-stdlib/celestial-pole-channel.fk -> 1111111)
;      The computable astronomy, native and exact: (jdn y m d) the Julian Day spine every
;      almanac agrees on (jdn 2000 1 1 = 2451545); (precession-degrees yr) how far the pole has
;      swung along its ~25,772-year circle since J2000 — why the north star is a procession,
;      not a fixed star; (tropical-sign-of / sidereal-sign-of) the SAME ecliptic degree read by
;      the Western moving zodiac and the Vedic fixed stars (one sky, two astrologies);
;      (pole-star-at year) who holds the pole in an era — Thuban for the pyramid builders,
;      Polaris now, Vega to come. Then the cross-belief faces of ONE pole-star body, riding the
;      engine: Polaris / Dhruva / al-Qutb / Cynosura / Beiji are five tongues sharing one
;      address; the engine confirms one body by content-address, not by surface. The structure
;      extends to sun, moon, and planets — each a body cell with as many faces as traditions
;      that named it. (north star + other celestial bodies across belief systems.)
;
;   3. INTERNAL FAMILY SYSTEMS  (form-stdlib/ifs-channel.fk -> tests/ifs-channel-band.fk 1111111)
;      Schwartz's parts-and-Self, where content-addressing reads the structure: Managers
;      (proactive) and Firefighters (reactive) are TWO STRATEGIES OF ONE protective role — they
;      share the protector address, so the engine calls them one cell; an exile is another. And
;      the eight qualities of Self (the 8 C's: Calm, Curiosity, Clarity, Compassion, Confidence,
;      Courage, Creativity, Connectedness) are eight FACES of one centre — they share Self's
;      address. The movement (ifs-guidance): no part is bad; lead from Self, witness the exile,
;      unburden it, and the protectors relax into their gifts.
;
;   4. THE ZODIAC, TWO TONGUES  (form-stdlib/zodiac-channel.fk -> tests/zodiac-channel-band.fk 1111111)
;      Twelve signs, fully seeded in both the Western (tropical: element, modality, keynote,
;      ruler) and Vedic (sidereal: rashi name, ruling graha) tongues. Aries and Mesha, Libra
;      and Tula, are one sign wearing two tongues — they share an address. What differs between
;      the systems is not the signs but which sign a degree falls in: that reduction lives in
;      celestial-pole-channel.fk; this channel speaks whichever index it returns. The two
;      compose: reduce a longitude (tropical or sidereal), then speak the sign.
;
;   5. CJK SYMBOLS  (form-stdlib/cjk-channel.fk -> tests/cjk-channel-band.fk 1111111)
;      Chinese and Japanese symbols in the encode / decode / translate space. A character is
;      the clearest "one cell, many tongues": the mountain glyph reads Chinese 'shan',
;      Japanese on 'san/sen', kun 'yama', English 'mountain' — one cell, the kanji on'yomi/
;      kun'yomi fact, translation by content-address. It adds the encoding the gates lacked:
;      characters COMPOSE from radicals (tree, then two trees = grove, three = forest), so a
;      shared radical-address returns the family — content-addressed composition. And it
;      bottoms out in the kernel's own ground: the I Ching line is yin or yang — nothing or
;      one, the states axiom — a trigram a 3-bit cell, a hexagram a 6-bit cell, 2^6 = 64 (the
;      gates). Glyphs ride in comments; runtime strings romanize until UTF-8 four-way string
;      parity is proven (a named next row).
;
; THE QUERY INTERFACE  (form-stdlib/channels-registry.fk -> tests/channels-registry-band.fk 1111111)
;
;   One surface over every system, native: registry-query (SPEAK a system's guidance for a
;   key), registry-translate (do two keys in two systems name one cell?), registry-decode
;   (every face, in every system, at one address), registry-systems / registry-found?. The
;   registry is nothing but a system-name -> table resolver plus the one engine — a new system
;   is one row in registry-channel, never a new query path. registry-decode 25 returns the
;   three faces of gate 25; registry-decode 5001 the mountain character in three tongues. The
;   celestial COMPUTATIONS (jdn, precession, pole-star-at, sign reduction) are a different
;   query shape (compute-from-arguments) and stay direct calls — named, not hidden. This is the
;   query interface's BODY; a /api/channels route or a web door is a thin carrier onto it
;   (BML/Form first, carrier-last), the next breath when a human door is wanted.
;
; HONESTY LANES
;
;   The COMPUTABLE recipes are empirical — a Julian Day is a Julian Day, a precession phase a
;   phase. The NAMES and their meanings are documented tradition, reported as attested, never
;   asserted as cosmology; guidance stays in the direct-experience / mystery lane and is never a
;   verdict (modality-lattices.form). Seeding is partial-by-design where a tradition's full table
;   is large (the 64); coverage is always queryable so a partial body never reads as complete. A
;   new gate, name, part, or tradition is a new ROW, not new code.
;
; OPENINGS NAMED AS NEXT ROWS  (closing recipes, not debts)
;
;   - the live ephemeris now computes the two luminaries and the karmic axis native, four-way:
;     ephemeris-sun.fk (the Sun's longitude, four cardinal points exact), ephemeris-moon.fk
;     (the Moon's longitude, sign, and lunar phase — verified at a real lunation's four
;     quarters), ephemeris-nodes.fk (Rahu/Ketu, retrograde, 180 apart). Gate activation lands
;     too: hd-mandala-wheel.fk carries the attested rave-mandala wheel (longitude -> gate),
;     closing date -> Sun longitude -> gate -> meaning. And the CAST is native: chart-cast.fk
;     composes the ephemeris + wheel + sign reduction into a date's edge-set (Sun/Moon/nodes
;     placed in signs and on gates, plus the lunar phase). The planets (Mercury..Saturn) are
;     the next rows (geocentric wants atan2); then synastry (two casts relating).
;   - pole-star selection is nearest-epoch; wrapping the full 25,772-year cycle is the next row.
;   - the 64, and each tradition's deeper tables (nakshatras, houses, lines/profiles), fill in by
;     row as their attested readings are grounded.
;   - CJK: the 214 Kangxi radicals and a wider character set fill in by row; carrying the glyph
;     itself in runtime strings (not only comments) waits on proven UTF-8 four-way string parity.
;   - the human door: a /api/channels route (BML/Form body) and a web surface onto
;     channels-registry.fk — built when a non-kernel reader is wanted, carrier-last.
;
; LINEAGE
;   kin: lc-cross-modal-unity (names are doors; one cell, many tongues — the governing teaching)
;        modality-lattices.form (every tradition a labeled lattice; the chart as edges; g8)
;        gematria-channel.fk / sanskrit-channel.fk / shamballa-channel.fk (the SPEAK/RUN parents)
;        word-roots.fk / prose-as-recipe.form (the WORD domain — CJK kin: derivation + lemma)
;   source: requested by Urs 2026-06-14; built on the channel pattern already in the body.
;           CJK symbols + the unified query interface added the same day, second breath.
